model

Class Datasource

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Datasource

  • public class Datasource
extends java.lang.Object
    This class handles all the queries to the database. It is constructed with the Singleton Design Pattern. This pattern involves a single class which is responsible to create an object while making sure that only single object gets created. This class provides a way to access its only object which can be accessed directly without need to instantiate the object of the class.
    Author:
    Sajmir Doko
